{
  "texts": [
    "PN pronuclear, AUC area under curve, CNN convolutional neural network, ANN artificial neural network, k-NN k-nearest neighbor.",
    "could be used as a preliminary screening tool with early recourse to diagnostic testing.",
    "Further, an ANN using semen parameters as inputs in 177 men was able to predict seminal plasma biochemical markers including fructose, zinc, and total protein content 43.",
    "The added value of these biochemical parameters over standard semen analyses is still unclear, but a number of omics-based markers in seminal fluid have been identified as helpful in determining fertilization prognosis in a cost-effective manner 44.",
    "Incorporating these techniques into the IVF clinic is challenging, namely due to initial set up costs and specialized techniques required for analysis."
  ]
}